    ('o-rain-come', 3, $$Ndo-ndo! Lilato heard it first. It sounded like a stone bouncing on the roof of the house. Lilato looked at Mayamiko but he didn’t look at her.$$, $$[{"role": "SFX", "text": "Ndo-ndo!", "bbox": [56.7, 68.3, 233.2, 108.3], "size": 40.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Lilato heard it first. It sounded like a stone bouncing on the roof of the house. Lilato looked at Mayamiko but he didn’t look at her.", "bbox": [56.7, 331.9, 367.1, 517.9], "size": 26.0}]$$),
