    ('oumas-amazing-flowers', 8, $$Please don’t pick Ouma’s flowers, Robyn! They won’t stay fresh very long.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Please don’t pick Ouma’s flowers, Robyn! They won’t stay fresh very long.", "bbox": [121.7, 215.7, 445.2, 363.6], "size": 28.0}]$$),
    ('oumas-amazing-flowers', 9, $$“I won’t pick them, Ouma,” says Robyn, even though she really wants to. She feels a little bit sad!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“I won’t pick them, Ouma,” says Robyn, even though she really wants to.", "bbox": [703.9, 188.6, 996.9, 336.6], "size": 28.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "She feels a little bit sad!", "bbox": [699.8, 362.7, 1001.0, 390.7], "size": 28.0}]$$),
    ('oumas-amazing-flowers', 10, $$Ouma doesn’t want Robyn to be sad. “Okay, Robyn,” says Ouma. “You can pick your favourite flower.”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Ouma doesn’t want Robyn to be sad.", "bbox": [157.0, 188.6, 409.9, 256.6], "size": 28.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Okay, Robyn,” says Ouma. “You can pick your favourite flower.”", "bbox": [141.8, 282.7, 425.1, 390.7], "size": 28.0}]$$),
    ('oumas-amazing-flowers', 11, $$“And I have an idea … Let’s plant more flowers together!”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“And I have an idea … Let’s plant more flowers together!”", "bbox": [715.7, 235.7, 985.1, 343.6], "size": 28.0}]$$),
    ('oumas-amazing-flowers', 12, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('oumas-amazing-flowers', 13, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('oyisa-and-the-giant-tree', 0, $$Oyisa loves to eat all kinds of fruit. She eats pears, grapes, oranges, and watermelon.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Oyisa loves to eat all kinds of fruit. She eats pears, grapes, oranges, and watermelon.", "bbox": [111.6, 244.7, 455.4, 332.7], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('oyisa-and-the-giant-tree', 1, $$She can eat a whole lot of fruit in no time at all.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "She can eat a whole lot of fruit in no time at all.", "bbox": [705.1, 258.3, 995.7, 321.3], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('oyisa-and-the-giant-tree', 2, $$But she doesn’t like the seeds. They get stuck in her teeth and taste bitter. Yuck!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "But she doesn’t like the seeds.", "bbox": [118.4, 228.8, 448.5, 252.8], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "They get stuck in her teeth and taste bitter. Yuck!", "bbox": [135.7, 292.8, 431.2, 350.8], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('oyisa-and-the-giant-tree', 3, $$Today, she’s eating a delicious, juicy pear. She spits the seeds out on the ground.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Today, she’s eating a delicious, juicy pear. She spits the seeds out on the ground.", "bbox": [679.4, 244.8, 1021.5, 332.8], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('oyisa-and-the-giant-tree', 4, $$A plant begins to grow between her feet. That’s strange, thinks Oyisa. What’s going on here?$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "A plant begins to grow between her feet.", "bbox": [157.9, 212.8, 409.0, 268.8], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "That’s strange, thinks Oyisa. What’s going on here?", "bbox": [128.0, 308.8, 437.9, 364.8], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('oyisa-and-the-giant-tree', 5, $$Suddenly, a tree shoots up high – with Oyisa perched on top! Oyisa needs to find a way down.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Suddenly, a tree shoots up high – with Oyisa perched on top!", "bbox": [91.1, 145.3, 475.8, 208.3], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Oyisa needs to find a way down.", "bbox": [740.2, 388.9, 905.7, 476.9], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('oyisa-and-the-giant-tree', 6, $$The look swing. branches like a umnand’ujingiwam”! she sings. “Jingijingi$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "The look swing. branches like a", "bbox": [353.8, 133.6, 505.1, 221.6], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "umnand’ujingiwam”! she sings.", "bbox": [737.0, 120.0, 1063.2, 316.5], "size": 40.4}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Jingijingi", "bbox": [630.0, 257.0, 735.9, 334.2], "size": 27.1}]$$),
    ('oyisa-and-the-giant-tree', 7, $$She swiiiiinggs to the next branch and meets a bird.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "She swiiiiinggs to the next branch and meets a bird.", "bbox": [645.1, 258.3, 1055.7, 321.3], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('oyisa-and-the-giant-tree', 8, $$The bird wants to build a cosy nest in her hair. “No way, Mr Bird!”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "The bird wants to build a cosy nest in her hair.", "bbox": [156.8, 260.8, 410.1, 316.8], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“No way, Mr Bird!”", "bbox": [896.1, 160.0, 1094.0, 224.5], "size": 27.2}]$$),
    ('oyisa-and-the-giant-tree', 9, $$On her way down, she spies a giant pear and climbs onto it. It sways in different directions, and this is the best feeling in the world!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "On her way down, she spies a giant pear and climbs onto it.", "bbox": [161.7, 180.8, 405.2, 268.8], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "It sways in different directions, and this is the best feeling in the world!", "bbox": [147.7, 308.8, 419.2, 396.8], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('oyisa-and-the-giant-tree', 10, $$“Oyisaaaa! your bath,” Mama It’s time calls. for “I’m coming!” shouts Oyisa from the tree.$$, $$[{"role": "SFX", "text": "“Oyisaaaa! your bath,” Mama It’s time calls. for “I’m coming!”", "bbox": [634.5, 52.2, 1020.5, 328.2], "size": 41.6}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "shouts Oyisa from the tree.", "bbox": [774.6, 393.6, 926.2, 449.6], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('oyisa-and-the-giant-tree', 11, $$What an adventure! Oyisa decides to start collecting seeds. Who knows what magic lies inside them?$$, $$[{"role": "SFX", "text": "What an adventure!", "bbox": [132.7, 210.3, 434.2, 243.3], "size": 33.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Oyisa decides to start collecting seeds. Who knows what magic lies inside them?", "bbox": [124.8, 281.3, 442.2, 369.3], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('oyisa-and-the-giant-tree', 12, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('oyisa-and-the-giant-tree', 13, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('pako-the-pigeon-disappears', 0, $$This is Pako the Pigeon. Pako goes, “Coo! Coo!”$$, $$[{"role": "SFX", "text": "This is Pako the Pigeon. Pako goes, “Coo! Coo!”", "bbox": [97.4, 208.5, 469.5, 386.9], "size": 46.5}]$$),
    ('pako-the-pigeon-disappears', 1, $$She flies and spreads out her wings. She loves to fly over Namwayi and Dairine’s house as they play crisscross every day.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "She flies and spreads out her wings.", "bbox": [57.2, 122.5, 305.0, 177.5], "size": 25.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "She loves to fly over Namwayi and Dairine’s house as they play crisscross every day.", "bbox": [716.6, 150.3, 984.2, 265.4], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('pako-the-pigeon-disappears', 2, $$Coo!Coo! Pako!Pako! Namwayi and Dairine love to imitate Pako. hands They spread the and house. run their around little$$, $$[{"role": "SFX", "text": "Coo!Coo! Pako!Pako!", "bbox": [145.1, 169.8, 481.1, 379.9], "size": 45.6}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Namwayi and Dairine love to imitate Pako. hands They spread the and house. run their around little", "bbox": [718.9, 113.5, 981.9, 275.5], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('pako-the-pigeon-disappears', 3, $$One fly over day, the Pako house did not as usual. Where could she be?$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "One fly over day, the Pako house did not as usual.", "bbox": [154.8, 244.6, 412.1, 329.6], "size": 25.0}, {"role": "SFX", "text": "Where could she be?", "bbox": [711.7, 251.5, 960.8, 339.5], "size": 40.0}]$$),
    ('pako-the-pigeon-disappears', 4, $$Dairine, Namwayi and the cat looked for Pako in the garden, but she was not there.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Dairine, Namwayi and the cat looked for Pako in the garden,", "bbox": [67.7, 148.9, 499.2, 203.9], "size": 25.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "but she was not there.", "bbox": [776.1, 139.7, 924.7, 194.7], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('pako-the-pigeon-disappears', 5, $$They looked in the sky and they could not see Pako anywhere. This made them very sad.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "They looked in the sky and they could not see Pako anywhere.", "bbox": [318.4, 133.3, 510.2, 248.3], "size": 25.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "This made them very sad.", "bbox": [623.6, 180.8, 813.2, 235.8], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('pako-the-pigeon-disappears', 6, $$Cat called to Pako: Meow! Meow !$$, $$[{"role": "SFX", "text": "Cat called to Pako: Meow! Meow !", "bbox": [642.7, 131.9, 1070.1, 467.8], "size": 47.9}]$$),
    ('pako-the-pigeon-disappears', 7, $$Cat heard Pako reply, and followed the sound. Coo! Coo!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Cat heard Pako reply, and followed the sound.", "bbox": [159.0, 153.2, 407.9, 238.2], "size": 25.0}, {"role": "SFX", "text": "Coo! Coo!", "bbox": [676.6, 94.4, 797.1, 181.6], "size": 43.0}]$$),
    ('pako-the-pigeon-disappears', 8, $$Oh no! Pako was caught in a thicket. Not to worry, I have soft and tender paws. See!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Oh no! Pako was caught in a thicket.", "bbox": [194.0, 154.6, 416.9, 209.6], "size": 25.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Not to worry, I have soft and tender paws. See!", "bbox": [832.7, 80.9, 1040.5, 165.9], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('pako-the-pigeon-disappears', 9, $$Cat gently took Pako to Namwayi and Dairine. They could see that Pako had hurt her wing.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Cat gently took Pako to Namwayi and Dairine. They could see that Pako had hurt her wing.", "bbox": [704.7, 221.2, 996.1, 353.2], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('pako-the-pigeon-disappears', 10, $$Pako’s wing was very sore, but the girls took good care of her. With Mum’s help, Namwayi and Dairine bandaged Pako’s wing to help her heal quickly.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Pako’s wing was very sore, but the girls took good care of her.", "bbox": [276.6, 119.2, 510.2, 234.2], "size": 25.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "With Mum’s help, Namwayi and Dairine bandaged Pako’s wing to help her heal quickly.", "bbox": [623.6, 157.4, 848.5, 302.4], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('pako-the-pigeon-disappears', 11, $$Coo! Coo! When Pako healed, she flew home. But she would fly to the girls’ window each morning. The would girls shout, “Good morning Pako!” Meow! Meow!$$, $$[{"role": "SFX", "text": "Coo! Coo!", "bbox": [347.8, 85.1, 455.9, 165.7], "size": 40.5}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "When Pako healed, she flew home. But she would fly to the girls’ window each morning.", "bbox": [119.5, 382.1, 447.4, 497.1], "size": 25.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "The would girls shout, “Good morning Pako!”", "bbox": [623.6, 107.8, 775.9, 252.8], "size": 25.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Meow! Meow!", "bbox": [684.9, 305.1, 799.5, 365.7], "size": 30.0}]$$),
    ('pako-the-pigeon-disappears', 12, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('pako-the-pigeon-disappears', 13, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('palesa-can-walk', 0, $$Palesa can’t sleep. It’s her birthday tomorrow. She’s one year old!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Palesa can’t sleep. It’s her birthday tomorrow. She’s one year old!", "bbox": [697.7, 258.8, 1003.3, 340.4], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('palesa-can-walk', 1, $$All her friends will bring her lots of presents.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "All her friends will bring her lots of presents.", "bbox": [717.4, 273.2, 983.5, 326.0], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('palesa-can-walk', 2, $$Seth will bring a... What will Seth bring? A rattle! And Sandile? A drum!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Seth will bring a... What will Seth bring? A rattle! And Sandile? A drum!", "bbox": [731.0, 228.9, 970.0, 368.1], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('palesa-can-walk', 3, $$But what about Aunty Mamsie? Oh, she’ll bring a cake, balloons, a trumpet, a talking doll, a computer, and ... and ... and ...$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "But what about Aunty Mamsie? Oh, she’ll bring a cake, balloons, a trumpet, a talking doll, a computer, and ... and ... and ...", "bbox": [643.4, 244.4, 1057.6, 354.8], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('palesa-can-walk', 4, $$LOOK! Palesa’s fast asleep...$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "LOOK! Palesa’s fast asleep...", "bbox": [688.9, 287.6, 1005.6, 311.6], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('palesa-can-walk', 5, $$TRII-IING-TRII-IING! “Happy birthday!” comes from the door. “Come in! Come in!” Mommy shouts.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "TRII-IING-TRII-IING! “Happy birthday!” comes from the door. “Come in! Come in!” Mommy shouts.", "bbox": [746.3, 50.0, 1005.5, 189.2], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('palesa-can-walk', 6, $$On her stool, Palesa’s eyes grow bigger and bigger.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "On her stool, Palesa’s eyes grow bigger and bigger.", "bbox": [703.1, 273.2, 997.9, 326.0], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('palesa-can-walk', 7, $$Over there, against the wall, the pile of toys grows and grows and grows.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Over there, against the wall, the pile of toys grows and grows and grows.", "bbox": [692.1, 258.8, 1008.8, 340.4], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('palesa-can-walk', 8, $$“Mine!” Palesa screams. “Mine!” she waves her angry arms. But everybody’s busy playing.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Mine!” Palesa screams. “Mine!” she waves her angry arms. But everybody’s busy playing.", "bbox": [656.0, 258.8, 1045.0, 340.4], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('palesa-can-walk', 9, $$“MINE!” And, with one big heave, pushes herself up. She goes and gathers the toys.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“MINE!” And, with one big heave, pushes herself up. She goes and gathers the toys.", "bbox": [662.6, 258.8, 1038.2, 340.4], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('palesa-can-walk', 10, $$Everybody stops. Then they all clap their hands. “Hurray! Palesa can walk!”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Everybody stops. Then they all clap their hands. “Hurray! Palesa can walk!”", "bbox": [682.3, 258.8, 1018.7, 340.4], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('palesa-can-walk', 11, $$Look! Now everyone is happy. Palesa is happy to play with her friends.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Look! Now everyone is happy. Palesa is happy to play with her friends.", "bbox": [629.4, 273.2, 1071.6, 326.0], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('palesa-can-walk', 12, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('palesa-can-walk', 13, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('samoosas', 0, $$Amir loves Grandma Rabiya’s kitchen. He loves the spices… the smells… and the sizzling sounds. Amir wants to learn to fold Grandma’s famous samoosas.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Amir loves Grandma Rabiya’s kitchen.", "bbox": [255.6, 109.3, 464.4, 157.7], "size": 22.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "He loves the spices… the smells… and the sizzling sounds.", "bbox": [238.0, 188.5, 482.0, 263.3], "size": 22.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Amir wants to learn to fold Grandma’s famous samoosas.", "bbox": [637.8, 148.9, 875.9, 223.7], "size": 22.0}]$$),
    ('samoosas', 1, $$Are samoosas square? No! laughs Amir.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Are samoosas square?", "bbox": [218.7, 99.7, 348.3, 157.2], "size": 28.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "No! laughs Amir.", "bbox": [748.5, 75.9, 912.8, 145.9], "size": 37.2}]$$),
    ('samoosas', 2, $$Are they circles? they’retriangles! No,Granny,$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Are they circles?", "bbox": [233.3, 433.6, 333.6, 500.9], "size": 28.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "they’retriangles! No,Granny,", "bbox": [670.5, 71.6, 918.7, 213.8], "size": 38.5}]$$),
    ('samoosas', 3, $$They sing Great- Great - Great - Grandma’s samoosa song. Chop the potatoes chop , chop , chop! Shake in the spices shake , shake, shake! Fold the samoosas fold, fold, fold!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "They sing Great- Great - Great - Grandma’s samoosa song.", "bbox": [113.0, 61.5, 453.9, 141.2], "size": 22.2}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Chop the potatoes chop , chop , chop! Shake in the spices shake , shake, shake!", "bbox": [710.9, 181.8, 1004.0, 353.7], "size": 28.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Fold the samoosas fold, fold, fold!", "bbox": [713.4, 380.2, 965.9, 454.1], "size": 27.9}]$$),
    ('samoosas', 4, $$Amir copies Grandma. Fold the dough once… Fold the dough twice…$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Amir copies Grandma. Fold the dough once… Fold the dough twice…", "bbox": [737.7, 424.2, 963.1, 511.6], "size": 22.0}]$$),
    ('samoosas', 5, $$Then fill it and fold it and paste it and done! But Amir’s samoosas look…$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Then fill it and fold it and paste it and done!", "bbox": [245.0, 147.2, 430.4, 233.8], "size": 25.5}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "But Amir’s samoosas look…", "bbox": [668.6, 177.3, 942.9, 199.3], "size": 22.0}]$$),
    ('samoosas', 6, $$…different. They’re not triangles! I don’t know what shape they are. But they’re not the same! I give up!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "…different.", "bbox": [189.3, 280.9, 377.6, 316.9], "size": 36.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "They’re not triangles! I don’t know what shape they are. But they’re not the same! I give up!", "bbox": [694.0, 70.5, 998.9, 224.1], "size": 27.8}]$$),
    ('samoosas', 7, $$Things don’t have to be the same, Amir. It’s the ddiiffffeerreennccee that makes the difference! Grandpa Farouk walks in and picks up a special-shaped samoosa …$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Things don’t have to be the same, Amir. It’s the ddiiffffeerreennccee that makes the difference!", "bbox": [84.3, 88.4, 482.6, 141.4], "size": 22.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Grandpa Farouk walks in and picks up a special-shaped samoosa …", "bbox": [671.9, 428.9, 1028.9, 477.3], "size": 22.0}]$$),
    ('samoosas', 8, $$CRUNCH! Hmmm, now that’s a tasty samoooooosa!$$, $$[{"role": "SFX", "text": "CRUNCH!", "bbox": [164.7, 384.7, 334.0, 464.7], "size": 55.8}, {"role": "SFX", "text": "Hmmm, now that’s a tasty samoooooosa!", "bbox": [696.5, 60.4, 1004.3, 120.5], "size": 30.5}]$$),
    ('samoosas', 9, $$You see! Your special-shaped samoosas are a hit. Highfive!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "You see! Your special-shaped samoosas are a hit.", "bbox": [277.5, 403.6, 457.4, 493.8], "size": 24.5}, {"role": "SFX", "text": "Highfive!", "bbox": [811.9, 158.9, 990.6, 276.1], "size": 56.8}]$$),
    ('samoosas', 10, $$From that day on Amir would chop , chop , chop! shake , shake, shake! fold, fold, fold! Just like Great-Great-Great-Grandma.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "From that day on Amir would chop , chop , chop! shake , shake, shake! fold, fold, fold! Just like Great-Great-Great-Grandma.", "bbox": [657.4, 89.2, 1043.4, 282.0], "size": 26.1}]$$),
    ('samoosas', 11, $$erew sasoomas s i tnere ffi d t i b e l tt il ! suoma f llits t ub Ha$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "erew sasoomas s i tnere ffi d t i b e l tt il ! suoma f llits t ub Ha", "bbox": [56.5, 153.8, 151.7, 410.3], "size": 16.2}]$$),
    ('samoosas', 12, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('samoosas', 13, $$How many shapes did you find?$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "How many shapes did you find?", "bbox": [120.7, 493.1, 446.2, 515.1], "size": 22.0}]$$),
    ('sams-treasures', 0, $$Sam and Dara were at the park. A shiny sparkle caught Sam’s eye.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Sam and Dara were at the park. A shiny sparkle caught Sam’s eye.", "bbox": [675.9, 169.3, 1024.9, 217.7], "size": 22.0}]$$),
    ('sams-treasures', 1, $$A crystal ball! A magic pearl! A treasure for Sam’s collection!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "A crystal ball! A magic pearl! A treasure for Sam’s collection!", "bbox": [123.6, 250.9, 443.3, 299.3], "size": 22.0}]$$),
    ('sams-treasures', 2, $$“That’s not treasure – that’s junk,” said Dara. She didn’t like the things Sam found.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“That’s not treasure – that’s junk,” said Dara.", "bbox": [109.5, 92.7, 457.4, 141.1], "size": 22.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "She didn’t like the things Sam found.", "bbox": [664.1, 476.8, 1036.7, 498.8], "size": 22.0}]$$),
    ('sams-treasures', 3, $$That was fine with Sam. “Time to go treasure hunting!” Off he went with his backpack.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "That was fine with Sam. “Time to go treasure hunting!”", "bbox": [695.8, 120.4, 1005.0, 168.8], "size": 22.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Off he went with his backpack.", "bbox": [693.0, 199.6, 1007.8, 221.6], "size": 22.0}]$$),
    ('sams-treasures', 4, $$Between the bushes Sam found a crown and a magic wand.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Between the bushes Sam found a crown and a magic wand.", "bbox": [120.1, 92.7, 446.8, 141.1], "size": 22.0}]$$),
    ('sams-treasures', 5, $$Under an old log he found monsters and creepy creatures. No thank you!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Under an old log he found monsters and creepy creatures. No thank you!", "bbox": [119.4, 145.4, 447.6, 229.8], "size": 22.0}]$$),
    ('sams-treasures', 6, $$Among the flowers Sam found a chest and a ring.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Among the flowers Sam found a chest and a ring.", "bbox": [693.3, 250.9, 1007.5, 299.3], "size": 22.0}]$$),
    ('sams-treasures', 7, $$In the stream Sam found a message in a bottle and a wise old wizard.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "In the stream Sam found a message in a bottle and a wise old wizard.", "bbox": [663.2, 325.2, 1037.6, 373.6], "size": 22.0}]$$),
    ('sams-treasures', 8, $$By the lamp post Sam found a sports car and a victory trophy. Time to show Dara all the treasures he had found!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "By the lamp post Sam found a sports car and a victory trophy. Time to show Dara all the treasures he had found!", "bbox": [627.0, 124.3, 1073.8, 199.1], "size": 22.0}]$$),
    ('sams-treasures', 9, $$Dara was crying. “I lost my ring,” said Dara. “I don’t know where I dropped it.”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Dara was crying. “I lost my ring,” said Dara. “I don’t know where I dropped it.”", "bbox": [113.0, 237.7, 453.9, 312.5], "size": 22.0}]$$),
    ('sams-treasures', 10, $$That sounded like something Sam had found. It was! It was Dara’s ring!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "That sounded like something Sam had found.", "bbox": [136.0, 61.5, 431.0, 110.0], "size": 22.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "It was! It was Dara’s ring!", "bbox": [724.2, 61.5, 976.7, 83.5], "size": 22.0}]$$),
    ('sams-treasures', 11, $$“Thank you, Sam! You DO find treasures!”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Thank you, Sam! You DO find treasures!”", "bbox": [638.5, 277.3, 1062.3, 299.3], "size": 22.0}]$$),
    ('sams-treasures', 12, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('sams-treasures', 13, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('scared-tumi', 0, $$My name is Tumi and I am scared.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "My name is Tumi and I am scared.", "bbox": [173.9, 260.9, 393.0, 315.9], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('scared-tumi', 1, $$Mama says it’s okay to be scared. “Everybody gets scared.”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Mama says it’s okay to be scared. “Everybody gets scared.”", "bbox": [111.6, 260.9, 455.3, 315.9], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('scared-tumi', 2, $$What if there is a monster under my bed?$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "What if there is a monster under my bed?", "bbox": [150.7, 260.9, 416.2, 315.9], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('scared-tumi', 3, $$“Then I will tell it to go away and NEVER come back.”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Then I will tell it to go away and NEVER come back.”", "bbox": [137.1, 260.9, 429.8, 315.9], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('scared-tumi', 4, $$What if there are eyes in the bath tub drain?$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "What if there are eyes in the bath tub drain?", "bbox": [171.5, 260.9, 395.4, 315.9], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('scared-tumi', 5, $$“Then your big sister, Kamo, will pull you out of the bath.”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Then your big sister, Kamo, will pull you out of the bath.”", "bbox": [133.6, 260.9, 433.3, 315.9], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('scared-tumi', 6, $$What if a whale swallows me at the beach?$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "What if a whale swallows me at the beach?", "bbox": [134.6, 260.9, 432.3, 315.9], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('scared-tumi', 7, $$“Then Kamo and I will swim into the whale’s mouth to rescue you.”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Then Kamo and I will swim into the whale’s mouth to rescue you.”", "bbox": [678.4, 457.7, 1076.5, 512.7], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('scared-tumi', 8, $$What if I can’t sing ABC and the other kids laugh at me?$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "What if I can’t sing ABC and the other kids laugh at me?", "bbox": [75.4, 111.7, 312.3, 196.7], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('scared-tumi', 9, $$“Then Teacher Jill will help you remember.”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Then Teacher Jill will help you remember.”", "bbox": [143.4, 260.4, 423.6, 315.4], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('scared-tumi', 10, $$What if I’m scared of going to the dentist tomorrow?$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "What if I’m scared of going to the dentist tomorrow?", "bbox": [145.7, 260.9, 421.2, 315.9], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('scared-tumi', 11, $$“I will be right there holding your hand.” Everybody gets scared. Mama says it’s okay.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“I will be right there holding your hand.”", "bbox": [75.6, 230.9, 491.4, 255.9], "size": 25.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Everybody gets scared. Mama says it’s okay.", "bbox": [163.7, 290.9, 403.2, 345.9], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('scared-tumi', 12, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('scared-tumi', 13, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('senzo-and-the-sun', 0, $$The morning sun creeps over the horizon and peeps through the leaves, waking Senzo. Gogo’s rooster shakes his wings, stretches his neck and crows. Koek-a-loek-a-loo!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "The morning sun creeps over the horizon and peeps through the leaves, waking Senzo.", "bbox": [623.6, 56.5, 988.6, 102.7], "size": 21.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Gogo’s rooster shakes his wings, stretches his neck and crows. Koek-a-loek-a-loo!", "bbox": [687.0, 132.1, 1077.3, 279.2], "size": 33.4}]$$),
    ('senzo-and-the-sun', 1, $$Senzo can crow too. Koek-a-loek-a-loo! Can you?$$, $$[{"role": "SFX", "text": "Senzo can crow too. Koek-a-loek-a-loo! Can you?", "bbox": [56.7, 67.7, 510.2, 295.0], "size": 34.0}]$$),
    ('senzo-and-the-sun', 2, $$The sun is bright and warm. Senzo is ready for school. He takes Gogo’s hand. The road is busy. Taxis zip past and toot their horns. Beep - beep! Beep - beep!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "The sun is bright and warm. Senzo is ready for school. He takes Gogo’s hand.", "bbox": [235.6, 106.1, 467.8, 177.5], "size": 21.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "The road is busy. Taxis zip past and toot their horns.", "bbox": [56.7, 206.9, 342.9, 253.1], "size": 21.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Beep - beep! Beep - beep!", "bbox": [224.7, 300.8, 467.7, 331.8], "size": 24.5}]$$),
    ('senzo-and-the-sun', 3, $$Senzo can toot too. Beep-beep! Beep-beep! Can you?$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Senzo can toot too.", "bbox": [630.7, 115.9, 837.2, 141.9], "size": 26.0}, {"role": "SFX", "text": "Beep-beep! Beep-beep! Can you?", "bbox": [671.0, 191.6, 1077.2, 328.9], "size": 39.3}]$$),
    ('senzo-and-the-sun', 4, $$The sun is high in the sky. School is over and Senzo’s friends play on the grass. They stretch out their arms and run down the hill. Weeeeeee!Weeeee!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "The sun is high in the sky. School is over and Senzo’s friends play on the grass.", "bbox": [56.7, 56.5, 478.0, 102.7], "size": 21.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "They stretch out their arms and run down the hill.", "bbox": [98.1, 132.1, 510.4, 153.1], "size": 21.0}, {"role": "SFX", "text": "Weeeeeee!Weeeee!", "bbox": [117.8, 202.2, 445.9, 280.1], "size": 48.1}]$$),
    ('senzo-and-the-sun', 5, $$Senzo can run too. Weeeeeee!Weeeee! Can you?$$, $$[{"role": "SFX", "text": "Senzo can run too. Weeeeeee!Weeeee! Can you?", "bbox": [619.1, 73.3, 1077.2, 327.5], "size": 35.8}]$$),
    ('senzo-and-the-sun', 6, $$The sun is low on the horizon, the sky is full of colour. The long day is nearly over and supper is finished. Gogo and Mama wash the dishes. Splish-splash! Splish- splash!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "The sun is low on the horizon, the sky is full of colour. The long day is nearly over and supper is finished.", "bbox": [56.7, 111.0, 503.7, 157.2], "size": 21.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Gogo and Mama wash the dishes. Splish-splash! Splish- splash!", "bbox": [623.6, 67.8, 1078.1, 142.6], "size": 26.5}]$$),
    ('senzo-and-the-sun', 7, $$Senzo can wash dishes too. Splish- splash! Splish- splash! Can you?$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Senzo can wash dishes too.", "bbox": [56.7, 86.3, 295.6, 107.3], "size": 21.0}, {"role": "SFX", "text": "Splish- splash! Splish- splash! Can you?", "bbox": [81.0, 167.2, 510.2, 330.3], "size": 42.7}]$$),
    ('senzo-and-the-sun', 8, $$The casting Senzo sun is long washed is dipping shadows. and under full and the tired. horizon, “It’s time to sleep,” says Mama. Shhhhhhhhh, shhhhhhhhhh. She holds Senzo close and rocks. She hushes him.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "The casting Senzo sun is long washed is dipping shadows. and under full and the tired. horizon, “It’s time to sleep,” says Mama.", "bbox": [56.7, 56.5, 367.7, 153.1], "size": 21.0}, {"role": "SFX", "text": "Shhhhhhhhh, shhhhhhhhhh.", "bbox": [633.0, 64.6, 1067.5, 121.8], "size": 36.9}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "She holds Senzo close and rocks. She hushes him.", "bbox": [245.0, 352.7, 510.3, 398.9], "size": 21.0}]$$),
    ('senzo-and-the-sun', 9, $$Senzo can hush too. Shhhhhhhhh,hhhh. shhhhh Can you?$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Senzo can hush too.", "bbox": [56.7, 84.7, 274.2, 110.7], "size": 26.0}, {"role": "SFX", "text": "Shhhhhhhhh,hhhh. shhhhh Can you?", "bbox": [70.2, 159.9, 510.2, 350.6], "size": 40.2}]$$),
    ('senzo-and-the-sun', 10, $$The sun has done her work for the day and she’s going to sleep. She pulls a blanket of darkness over herself to keep warm. The sun dreams.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "The sun has done her work for the day and she’s going to sleep.", "bbox": [56.7, 56.5, 374.0, 102.7], "size": 21.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "She pulls a blanket of darkness over herself to keep warm. The sun dreams.", "bbox": [56.7, 132.1, 510.2, 229.9], "size": 25.5}]$$),
    ('senzo-and-the-sun', 11, $$Senzo can dream too. Can you?$$, $$[{"role": "SFX", "text": "Senzo can dream too. Can you?", "bbox": [83.6, 108.1, 490.8, 217.5], "size": 41.5}]$$),
    ('senzo-and-the-sun', 12, $$$$, $$[]$$),
