    ('tata-comes-home', 0, $$Every Friday after school, Daluxolo stands with his arms leaning over the front gate, waiting...$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Every Friday after school, Daluxolo stands with his arms leaning over the front gate, waiting...", "bbox": [687.4, 89.7, 1032.6, 188.0], "size": 21.0}]$$),
    ('tata-comes-home', 1, $$Daaaaaaaalllllliiiiiiiiiiiii! His friends keep calling him to play ball with them at the dusty soccer field down the road but he keeps saying no. DDaaaali!$$, $$[{"role": "SFX", "text": "Daaaaaaaalllllliiiiiiiiiiiii!", "bbox": [233.6, -206.2, 674.0, -38.9], "size": 55.7}, {"role": "SFX", "text": "His friends keep calling him to play ball with them at the dusty soccer field down the road but he keeps saying no. DDaaaali!", "bbox": [93.5, 54.2, 476.1, 251.9], "size": 45.8}]$$),
    ('tata-comes-home', 2, $$That’s because someone special is coming … every weekend Tata comes home.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "That’s because someone special is coming … every weekend Tata comes home.", "bbox": [725.5, 115.9, 1045.2, 279.7], "size": 41.2}]$$),
    ('tata-comes-home', 3, $$He cranes his neck towards the main road, eagerly waiting to see the moment when Tata’s white VW Beetle turns into his street.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "He cranes his neck towards the main road, eagerly waiting to see the moment when Tata’s white VW Beetle turns into his street.", "bbox": [623.6, 51.4, 1043.9, 162.4], "size": 21.0}]$$),
    ('tata-comes-home', 4, $$As soon as it turns the corner, Dali runs to the home car in so Tata’s he can car. drive the rest of the way Beep! Beeep!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "As soon as it turns the corner, Dali runs to the home car in so Tata’s he can car. drive the rest of the way", "bbox": [69.8, 61.3, 487.0, 142.3], "size": 21.0}, {"role": "SFX", "text": "Beep! Beeep!", "bbox": [633.6, 93.3, 842.1, 246.0], "size": 80.0}]$$),
    ('tata-comes-home', 5, $$“Hello Dali my boy,” Tata yells with excitement, as he opens the door. “Hop in!”$$, $$[{"role": "SFX", "text": "“Hello Dali my boy,” Tata yells with excitement, as he opens the door. “Hop in!”", "bbox": [226.5, 63.5, 539.1, 307.1], "size": 37.9}]$$),
    ('tata-comes-home', 6, $$When Tata is home, he and Dali always have so much fun together, starting with their favourite meal cooked by Mama – pap, wors and gravy.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "When Tata is home, he and Dali always have so much fun together,", "bbox": [278.5, 59.9, 514.0, 140.9], "size": 21.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "starting with their favourite meal cooked by Mama – pap, wors and gravy.", "bbox": [623.6, 120.2, 839.0, 303.4], "size": 41.2}]$$),
    ('tata-comes-home', 7, $$On Saturday morning, they start their day with a short jog around the neighbourhood.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "On Saturday morning, they start their day with a short jog around the neighbourhood.", "bbox": [700.6, 197.4, 1000.2, 278.4], "size": 21.0}]$$),
    ('tata-comes-home', 8, $$Then after lunch, Tata teaches Dali how to play card games.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Then after lunch, Tata teaches Dali how to play card games.", "bbox": [637.9, 97.7, 857.4, 178.7], "size": 21.0}]$$),
    ('tata-comes-home', 9, $$In the afternoon, Dali loves watching Tata polish his shoes while whistling to his favourite songs on the radio.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "In the afternoon, Dali loves watching Tata polish his shoes while whistling to his favourite songs on the radio.", "bbox": [133.6, 102.4, 433.4, 213.4], "size": 21.0}]$$),
    ('tata-comes-home', 10, $$Sunday is the saddest day when they have to say goodbye because Tata must go back to work.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Sunday is the saddest day when they have to say goodbye because Tata must go back to work.", "bbox": [99.5, 412.8, 447.4, 493.8], "size": 21.0}]$$),
    ('tata-comes-home', 11, $$But Dali does not stay sad for long because he knows that on Friday, Tata comes home.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "But Dali does not stay sad for long because he knows that on Friday, Tata comes home.", "bbox": [668.9, 226.4, 1031.9, 335.4], "size": 34.5}]$$),
